I have a lot of rage at the world right now. The vaccine debacle is just the cherry on this shit cake.

Wisconsin Republicans are horrendous, & I will do everything in my power to ensure that none are re-elected, you snide, hypocritical people.

You aren’t leaders. It’s shameful.
Republicans wanted herd immunity.. which is, the same as expecting the entire population of Wisconsin to die. But are concerned and not taking vaccine due to possible containments in  vaccines

VAERS report 1243516:
16yo Female, Wisconsin
Collapsed at home and died. Heart failure 9 days after Pfizer vaccination.

Why was this report removed from VAERS after 04-30-2021?

VAERS report 1218081:
17yo Female, Wisconsin
Heart failure 8 days after Pfizer vaccination.

Why was this report removed from VAERS after 04-30-2021?

The latest @DHSWI data shows 63.5% of people living in #Wisconsin have received at least one dose of the vaccine; 59.7% have completed the vaccine series. In #Milwaukee County, 60.5% of residents have received at least one dose.
